io.micronaut.build

Class DockerfileMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • io.micronaut.build.AbstractDockerMojo
        • io.micronaut.build.DockerfileMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    @Mojo(name="dockerfile",
      requiresDependencyResolution=COMPILE_PLUS_RUNTIME)
public class DockerfileMojo
extends AbstractDockerMojo

    Generates a Dockerfile depending on the packaging and micronaut.runtime properties. 

    mvn mn:dockerfile -Dpackaging=docker-native -Dmicronaut.runtime=lambda
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Álvaro Sánchez-Mariscal
